name: Untitled Tree Concept
description:
Small concept for a game in which you are a tree.

I started this concept to know how Corgi Engine works in Unity,

This is a project a grew tired of an decided I had to wrap and move on to something else. The webGL build killed a lot of the visual flavor it had in a Windows build.

It's uploaded here to remind me it's ok quit on a project when it is going nowhere.
